StringValues.16: A note from Nasun ibn Tifar in the North Yaraq Outpost, for delivery to Ahyara in the East Yaraq Outpost.
StringValues.15: A note from Nasun ibn Tifar for delivery to Ahyara.

Pages.Text:
** For delivery to Ahyara in the East Yaraq Outpost

Lovely Mara,

We have had news of fortune's munificence to you.  Accept our compliments in this happy time.

- Nasun ibn Tifar
